      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. I don't want it to feel like modern people just pretending to be old; it needs to feel visceral. Could you actually write out a short snippet of the dialogue? Maybe three or four characters sitting around a table in a dimly lit office. I want to see how they'd actually phrase their concerns about the \"unrest\" and how they'd describe the people they're worried about to justify their actions. I need that gritty, period-accurate tension.",
